&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD&#34;&gt;	//fprintf(stderr, &#34;This last malloc will be served from the remainder code and will return the av-&gt;top+8 injected before\n&#34;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5&#34;&gt;&amp;#125;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这个示例是将一个全局变量给复写了，也提到了&lt;code&gt;This PoC works also with ASLR enabled.But this technique RELRO must be disabled&lt;/code&gt; 也就是说如果想要修改got表，就不能开启RELRO&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2调试程序-5&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#2调试程序-5&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 2.调试程序&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;1执行到31行打印区间变量地址&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#1执行到31行打印区间变量地址&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 1.执行到31行，打印区间变量地址&lt;/h3&gt;
